txt.en: Return to Khanâg Valoyar in An Shêru
Talk to Rahâzi at TBD in Khanâg Valoyar
Talk to Rahâzi in Khanâg Valoyar and sneak aboard the next waggon to depart
According to what you learned in Emax Dûl, the waggons for TBD depart from Khanâg Valoyar.
Your companions assemble at TBD to discuss these fresh dangers.
Rahâzi is at TBD in Khanâg Valoyar.
Rahâzi is at TBD in Khanâg Valoyar. She has identified the next waggon to depart, and is prepared to sneak aboard it with you.
Your companions assemble at TBD to discuss these fresh dangers.
Glorfindel will remain in Idagâl to stand against the Thardúth
Ulishár will remain in Idagâl to stand alongside Têrkar's Travellers
Rahâzi will journey with you and oppose this last evil of Sauron
With dangers looming in two directions, the time has come to make a difficult choice: some must remain in Idagâl to oppose the Thardúth, and some must return north to combat this last evil of Sauron.
Fortunately, there is no sign of the Temámir who accosted you during your last visit
